content:
morgan Holbrook Copy EditorSeptember  

If youve ever craved freshbaked chocolate chip cookies at  a.m. you might be in luck PERIOD

Insomnia Cookies a chain known for delivering cookies to college campuses until  a.m. has recently opened a store in Tinseltown Plaza on Southside Boulevard PERIOD The store is inconspicuously tucked in a newly constructed complex between the Tinseltown parking lot and Wild Wing Cafe PERIOD

If that news wasnt sweet enough the store is also running a great deal to mark the occasion PERIOD

The stores official grand opening was Friday September  but customers who visit the store for the next few days can still receive a coupon for a free instore cookie PERIOD
